# 0.1.0
- feat: initial release of stable-diffusion.cpp addon for SD1.x, SD2.x, SDXL, SD3, and FLUX model inference
- feat: GPU acceleration via CUDA and Vulkan backends (Linux), Metal (macOS), CPU fallback
- feat: dynamic ggml backend loading for Android (GGML_BACKEND_DL) with libqvac-diffusion-ggml-* naming to avoid system conflicts
- feat: vcpkg-based build system with clang override triplet for Linux and PIC static linking
- feat: build:cuda and build:vulkan npm scripts for GPU-specific builds
